
  2005-01-12 Version 0.6-0
    *  Utilization of Namespace mechanism (introducted in R 1.7.0).
    *  A new argument in the 'plot.fdata' function has been added
       ('separator').
    *  The simulation functions have been modified to accept functional
       spaces of dimension greater than twice the number of discretization
       points.
    *  A new function 'interpol.matrix' is used to calculate the matrix
       giving the linear interpolation of values of a function.
    *  The help files are completed.

  2002-02-19 Version 0.5-2
    *  Add of the theoritical.coef function.

  2001-12-04 Version 0.5-1
    *  First release of the library.
